news_header: Healthcare workers and profits increased significantly in the health sector.
news_text: Healthcare workers grew by 60% compared to the same period last year. The Health Service Company reported an adjusted operating profit of approximately EUR 34 million for July-September, also reflecting a 60% increase from the previous year. Additionally, the net sales of the health office reached around EUR 296 million, marking an increase of over 5% year-on-year.
